ygData.messageBody:
Now the treants in S karana you can make that much cash, maybe in a good
group you can do it at 20, but they range up to 26 or 27. That's the best
hunting spot I've found in the mid 20's (pretty good up to 30 also). And
even there I might make 100 pp in 6-8 hours. You take negative faction hits
against Qeynos guards (guess they're all tree-huggers) so be warned.

Oglug ~Hand of Chaos~




Message text written by INTERNET:warriors_eq@onelist.com
>I have a couple hunting grounds although some of them aren't really well
known and I don't plan on telling anybody. On a very good day I can rake in
200pp but that's my best day and that's a full 8 hours of game time. It
really isn't hard to gain money past!
level 20.
